high_descs: Turn right and go to the coffee maker
Grab the mug in the coffee maker
Turn right and go to the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave and then take it out
Back up from the counter and look up at the cabinets
Put the mug in the left cabinet above the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot mug in a cabinet

high_descs: Turn right then walk forward turn right facing the counter beside the coffee maker
Pick up the mug on the coffee maker
Turn right then move forward face the microwave on your left
Open the microwave heat up the - then take it out and close the microwave
Turn left then move backwards to see the cabinet above the microwave
Open the cabinet and put in the mug then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the cabinet

high_descs: Go right and then turn right again to face the counter where the coffee maker is.
Pick the mug up from under the coffee maker.
Move to the right and face the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick the mug up again and shut the door.
Move back and look up to face the cabinet above the microwave on the left.
Put the mug in the cabinet above the microwave and on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug in the microwave.
